room_title: Escape room "Escape from Myth Room" by San Jose Room Escape in San Jose
room_address: 1620 Oakland Road, Suite D203 San Jose, CA 95131
room_description: You wake up one day and find yourself locked in a cramped room. Silence surrounds you. Only the clock is ticking and your heart is pondering. Can you meet the challenge of finding your BART ticket and escape in time for freedom? Whether you have played Escape Game before, this Myth-themed room is the place to start a new adventure.
